{"tid":1219132,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[台灣朋友叫我代佢講聲多謝]港獨未成，林鄭已為台獨之路立下大功！","createTime":"2019-06-13T18:00:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-06T20:50:21.000Z","uid":185935,"like":39,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"dfa5f54cbbd4fe4da8fe2ef573ba1d16a495c89d","tid":1219132,"uid":185935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T18:00:05.000Z","msg":"下年台灣大選，因為民調數字一直都唔好，本來蔡英文都仲未知會唔會代表民進黨出選。<br />\n<br />\n但因為近日香港引渡條例，蔡英文公開表明同支持香港人，同時支持度大增，好多台灣人都醒覺唔想咁樣發大財<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://theinitium.com/article/20190613-taiwan-tsai-hongkong-extradition-bill-protest/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftheinitium.com%2Farticle%2F20190613-taiwan-tsai-hongkong-extradition-bill-protest%2F&d=dLzfXDqznxc4YuOEPdKADRphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=bbb8ceaf\" target=\"_blank\">https://theinitium.com/article/20190613-taiwan-tsai-hongkong-extradition-bill-protest/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/amp/chinese-news-48621404\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Famp%2Fchinese-news-48621404&d=dLzfXDqznxc4YuOEPdKADRphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=0834d30d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Famp%2Fchinese-news-48621404&h=93046c91\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/amp/chinese-news-48621404</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n林鄭未做到港獨之母前可以已經成為台獨之母！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">大家一定要廣傳，傳到阿爺都聽到呀～<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"5aa8d012f3d4f8da30fbc25a413334deb8a7d1ec","tid":1219132,"uid":3295,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T20:19:50.000Z","msg":"依個真，見到藍營節目係度屌話蔡英文咁勝之不武就好想笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢地收左人錢又唔敢話反中<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54712ffb223f1656a5c78